WEBVTT

00:01:21.240 --> 00:01:22.000
Boss.

00:01:22.880 --> 00:01:23.400
Boss.

00:01:23.400 --> 00:01:24.600
Something happened.

00:01:25.039 --> 00:01:25.440
Boss.

00:01:25.440 --> 00:01:26.840
Something big happened.

00:01:29.200 --> 00:01:30.720
That's a good thing.

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:32.960
When something happens,

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:34.080
people die.

00:01:34.759 --> 00:01:36.080
When people die,

00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:37.720
someone will cry.

00:01:38.360 --> 00:01:39.560
When they cry,

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:42.240
they come here to spend money.

00:01:43.120 --> 00:01:44.960
They are bringing us wealth.

00:01:46.600 --> 00:01:47.930
Don't just stand there.

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:50.080
Get ready to welcome the guests.

00:02:06.080 --> 00:02:06.810
Captain Sun.

00:02:10.160 --> 00:02:10.690
Mr. Wang.

00:02:11.080 --> 00:02:11.880
Any findings?

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:14.970
You saw it too, Captain Sun.

00:02:15.360 --> 00:02:15.760
This

00:02:15.760 --> 00:02:16.400
explosion,

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:17.079
collapse,

00:02:17.160 --> 00:02:17.760
flying rocks,

00:02:17.760 --> 00:02:18.320
and dust

00:02:18.840 --> 00:02:20.770
have severely damaged the traces.

00:02:21.200 --> 00:02:23.120
However, on the detonating cord,

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:23.880
detonator,

00:02:23.960 --> 00:02:25.079
and bomb fragments left at the scene,

00:02:25.079 --> 00:02:27.210
we found Ma Jinguang's fingerprints.

00:02:36.120 --> 00:02:36.780
Take a look.

00:02:39.800 --> 00:02:40.600
Furthermore,

00:02:40.920 --> 00:02:41.600
tests show

00:02:41.880 --> 00:02:43.600
the explosive composition is identical to

00:02:43.600 --> 00:02:45.000
the one that killed Zhang Biao.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:46.640
So our preliminary deduction is

00:02:46.640 --> 00:02:48.000
that the bomb was made,

00:02:48.040 --> 00:02:50.370
installed, and detonated by Ma Jinguang.

00:02:51.400 --> 00:02:52.530
Only Ma Jinguang's?

00:02:53.480 --> 00:02:54.720
Other than Wang Hongjia,

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:55.240
Yan Mi,

00:02:55.320 --> 00:02:56.040
and Ma Jinguang,

00:02:56.040 --> 00:02:58.079
were there no traces of a fourth person at the scene?

00:02:58.079 --> 00:02:59.079
Not at the moment.

00:02:59.160 --> 00:03:00.360
Keep investigating.

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:02.080
Since Yan Mi said

00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:04.760
Ma Jinguang didn't commit Wang Hongjia's murder,

00:03:04.760 --> 00:03:05.560
then that day,

00:03:05.840 --> 00:03:08.320
there must have been a fourth person at the scene.

00:03:08.320 --> 00:03:10.380
Leave no stone unturned to find them.

00:03:10.760 --> 00:03:11.490
Captain Sun.

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:12.640
Keep looking.

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:13.360
Be thorough.

00:03:13.360 --> 00:03:13.890
Yes, sir.

00:03:22.640 --> 00:03:24.600
If Ma Jinguang didn't do these,

00:03:24.920 --> 00:03:27.360
why did the killer insist on framing him?

00:03:29.520 --> 00:03:31.380
But no matter how cunning a fox is,

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:32.579
it still has a tail.

00:03:35.560 --> 00:03:37.200
Strict law enforcement.

00:03:37.760 --> 00:03:39.040
In the cabin on the mountain,

00:03:39.040 --> 00:03:40.800
we found Ma Jinguang's DNA

00:03:40.800 --> 00:03:42.130
and explosive residue.

00:03:42.440 --> 00:03:43.280
After testing,

00:03:43.280 --> 00:03:44.160
these residues

00:03:44.160 --> 00:03:46.760
have the same composition as those in Zhang Biao's bombing case.

00:03:46.760 --> 00:03:47.960
It can be reasonably inferred.

00:03:47.960 --> 00:03:49.760
Ma Jinguang was making explosives

00:03:49.760 --> 00:03:50.490
in the cabin.

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:52.280
Combined with

00:03:52.280 --> 00:03:53.760
some of his previous confessions,

00:03:53.760 --> 00:03:54.440
we can

00:03:54.440 --> 00:03:55.720
reasonably conclude that

00:03:55.720 --> 00:03:57.120
Ma Jinguang was

00:03:57.120 --> 00:03:58.360
the explosives provider for the Zhou Gang bombing five years ago,

00:03:58.360 --> 00:03:59.200
as well as the current

00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:00.120
Zhang Biao

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:00.920
bombing case.

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:04.000
Just providing explosives?

00:04:05.760 --> 00:04:07.440
Did he specifically

00:04:08.080 --> 00:04:09.680
commit the crimes directly?

00:04:11.920 --> 00:04:13.040
Evidence shows

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:16.370
that the one who murdered Wang Hongjia

00:04:16.440 --> 00:04:17.370
couldn't be him.

00:04:17.760 --> 00:04:19.720
Although in this mine explosion,

00:04:19.839 --> 00:04:20.959
the clothes he wore

00:04:21.120 --> 00:04:22.880
and those captured on surveillance

00:04:22.880 --> 00:04:25.010
during the kidnapping of Wang Hongjia

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:26.160
are exactly the same,

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:27.200
the current evidence

00:04:27.200 --> 00:04:28.860
cannot form a complete chain.

00:04:29.240 --> 00:04:30.120
Furthermore,

00:04:31.520 --> 00:04:32.440
currently, both Wang Hongjia

00:04:32.440 --> 00:04:33.300
and Ma Jinguang

00:04:33.920 --> 00:04:35.440
are in a deep coma.

00:04:36.200 --> 00:04:37.930
Until we get more information,

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:39.159
we cannot make

00:04:39.800 --> 00:04:41.130
any further judgments.

00:04:48.560 --> 00:04:50.159
We haven't found the killer.

00:04:51.640 --> 00:04:54.300
Instead, we're finding more and more problems.

00:04:55.520 --> 00:04:56.850
Yan Mi also got injured,

00:04:58.320 --> 00:04:59.240
guys.

00:05:00.760 --> 00:05:03.290
I've also worked in criminal investigation.

00:05:04.600 --> 00:05:06.280
I have walked all the paths

00:05:06.280 --> 00:05:07.410
you are walking now.

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:10.200
So I can understand

00:05:12.280 --> 00:05:13.400
everyone's hardships,

00:05:13.400 --> 00:05:14.760
and I keep them in mind.

00:05:15.400 --> 00:05:17.000
But coming back to the point.

00:05:17.520 --> 00:05:18.800
As a police officer,

00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:22.040
if you can't solve cases,

00:05:22.040 --> 00:05:23.560
no matter how much hardship you endure

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:24.800
or how many injuries you suffer,

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:26.240
what is the use?

00:05:27.760 --> 00:05:29.480
I just don't believe it.

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:34.040
I don't believe there is such a perfect crime.

00:05:34.640 --> 00:05:35.700
As long as he did it,

00:05:35.760 --> 00:05:37.480
he will definitely leave traces.

00:05:37.480 --> 00:05:39.010
Why can't we find anything?

00:05:39.159 --> 00:05:41.040
Because our work isn't detailed enough.

00:05:41.040 --> 00:05:42.040
So I suggest

00:05:42.159 --> 00:05:43.400
everyone start from scratch

00:05:43.400 --> 00:05:45.240
and review all the case details.

00:05:45.240 --> 00:05:46.920
We must be thorough and detailed.

00:05:46.920 --> 00:05:48.560
Don't miss anything.

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:49.890
I am counting on you all.

00:05:57.120 --> 00:05:57.780
Chief Zhao,

00:05:58.120 --> 00:05:59.180
there's something

00:05:59.320 --> 00:06:00.580
I hope you can approve.

00:06:02.920 --> 00:06:03.980
What are you doing?

00:06:04.640 --> 00:06:06.160
Are you trying to undermine me?

00:06:06.160 --> 00:06:07.620
I just finished speaking,

00:06:08.160 --> 00:06:09.520
and you're already trying to back out?

00:06:09.520 --> 00:06:10.720
I will never back out.

00:06:10.920 --> 00:06:12.880
I will definitely investigate this case to the end.

00:06:12.880 --> 00:06:13.960
Then I still don't understand.

00:06:13.960 --> 00:06:15.080
What do you mean by this?

00:06:15.080 --> 00:06:15.940
Five years ago,

00:06:15.960 --> 00:06:17.960
I was the lead investigator of Zhou Gang's case.

00:06:17.960 --> 00:06:18.760
Now we found

00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:21.960
that the chain of evidence is indeed flawed.

00:06:21.960 --> 00:06:23.620
I should be held accountable.

00:06:24.240 --> 00:06:26.100
Whether you are held accountable

00:06:26.360 --> 00:06:27.400
or how you are held accountable,

00:06:27.400 --> 00:06:29.000
is not for you to worry about.

00:06:29.080 --> 00:06:29.760
For you,

00:06:29.760 --> 00:06:30.600
the most important thing right now

00:06:30.600 --> 00:06:32.200
is how you view your mistakes

00:06:32.280 --> 00:06:34.760
and whether you have the courage and determination to correct them.

00:06:34.760 --> 00:06:36.220
Learn from your mistakes,

00:06:36.360 --> 00:06:37.280
take honesty as a warning,

00:06:37.280 --> 00:06:39.080
and don't make another mistake.

00:06:40.640 --> 00:06:41.120
Chief Zhao,

00:06:41.120 --> 00:06:41.440
alright,

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:41.760
I...

00:06:41.760 --> 00:06:43.080
Stop saying useless things.

00:06:43.080 --> 00:06:44.810
Just focus on solving the case.

00:06:49.920 --> 00:06:51.180
By the end of the month,

00:06:51.640 --> 00:06:53.170
if I don't catch the killer,

00:06:53.920 --> 00:06:55.520
I will take off this uniform.

00:06:58.480 --> 00:07:00.600
This is what was on Wang Hongjia's body.

00:07:00.600 --> 00:07:00.960
Yes.

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:03.280
This is the mycelium of a fungus called Mycena haematopus.

00:07:03.280 --> 00:07:05.920
It can emit a pale green fluorescence in the dark.

00:07:05.920 --> 00:07:07.380
But the light is very weak,

00:07:07.520 --> 00:07:09.580
so it's hard to see with the naked eye.

00:07:10.440 --> 00:07:11.640
Glowing mushrooms.

00:07:12.520 --> 00:07:14.280
After going to such great lengths,

00:07:14.280 --> 00:07:16.440
what exactly is the killer trying to say?

00:07:16.440 --> 00:07:17.440
Come look at this.

00:07:21.840 --> 00:07:24.280
The killer cut open Wang Hongjia's skin

00:07:24.640 --> 00:07:26.720
and attached mycelium to the wound,

00:07:27.120 --> 00:07:29.680
giving it the appearance of a scar.

00:07:30.760 --> 00:07:32.320
And this Mycena haematopus

00:07:32.480 --> 00:07:34.960
is also known as the bleeding fairy helmet.

00:07:35.920 --> 00:07:37.120
It has a unique trait.

00:07:37.360 --> 00:07:38.159
When damaged,

00:07:38.320 --> 00:07:39.400
