When did you get here?

00:11:09.160 --> 00:11:10.960
We don't allow visitors for now.

00:11:12.600 --> 00:11:13.320
I'm sorry.

00:11:15.440 --> 00:11:15.960
Mi.

00:11:16.760 --> 00:11:17.600
Get well soon.

00:11:18.680 --> 00:11:21.540
The bad guys are still waiting for you to catch them.

00:11:23.960 --> 00:11:25.090
Sorry to bother you.

00:11:41.760 --> 00:11:42.920
Thank you, Uncle.

00:11:49.800 --> 00:11:50.840
Thank you, Uncle.

00:11:51.920 --> 00:11:52.280
Here.

00:11:52.400 --> 00:11:52.880
Thank you.

00:11:52.880 --> 00:11:53.810
You're welcome.

00:12:05.520 --> 00:12:05.880
Wait.

