00:12:24.480 --> 00:12:25.210
Hey, Master.

00:12:26.840 --> 00:12:27.840
I'm speechless.

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:10.000
Old Yan.

00:13:11.440 --> 00:13:12.400
Is your injury healed?

00:13:12.400 --> 00:13:14.260
You shouldn't be running around.

00:13:14.680 --> 00:13:15.400
Come back with me

00:13:15.400 --> 00:13:16.130
and recover.

00:13:16.160 --> 00:13:16.920
I'm fine.

00:13:17.520 --> 00:13:18.360
I can walk,

00:13:18.360 --> 00:13:19.220
and I can think.

