Me?

00:16:39.960 --> 00:16:42.620
Ma Jinguang provided the bomb without knowing.

00:16:43.120 --> 00:16:44.920
This is actually not the truth.

00:16:45.960 --> 00:16:47.240
At best, it's just

00:16:47.840 --> 00:16:48.600
an answer,

00:16:49.320 --> 00:16:50.780
an answer that makes me see

00:16:51.360 --> 00:16:52.640
how cowardly I am.

00:16:53.400 --> 00:16:55.000
I held on to those doubts

00:16:55.320 --> 00:16:57.600
because I dared not face the fact

00:16:57.920 --> 00:17:00.000
that I handed the car keys to our master.

00:17:00.000 --> 00:17:01.200
The real killer I hate

00:17:01.320 --> 00:17:02.320
is actually the me

00:17:02.440 --> 00:17:04.900
who should have been in the car but survived.

00:17:05.359 --> 00:17:07.319
Closing the case back then wasn't wrong.

00:17:07.319 --> 00:17:07.920
It was me

00:17:08.280 --> 00:17:10.520
who didn't want to accept this simple cruelty.

00:17:10.520 --> 00:17:12.319
Now we've found the real killer.

00:17:12.800 --> 00:17:13.720
Living to bear

00:17:13.720 --> 00:17:14.680
this guilt

00:17:16.319 --> 00:17:17.040
requires more courage

00:17:17.040 --> 00:17:18.119
than dying.

00:17:19.960 --> 00:17:20.619
From now on,

00:17:20.800 --> 00:17:22.560
bear the responsibilities you should bear.

00:17:22.560 --> 00:17:23.800
Do what you should do.

00:17:24.359 --> 00:17:26.079
This is the best explanation

00:17:26.640 --> 00:17:27.480
for our master, his wife,

00:17:27.480 --> 00:17:28.480
and Guannan.

00:17:29.320 --> 00:17:29.920
Yan.

00:17:30.280 --> 00:17:32.600
This reconciliation you've reached with yourself

00:17:32.600 --> 00:17:34.320
is the most precious growth.

00:17:35.120 --> 00:17:37.160
I hope you and Sun Xun can take our master's

00:17:37.160 --> 00:17:38.800
unfinished glory

00:17:39.720 --> 00:17:40.450
and carry on.

00:17:52.360 --> 00:17:53.360
Let's get back to the case.

00:17:53.360 --> 00:17:55.320
We identified the mycelium on Wang Hongjia.

00:17:55.320 --> 00:17:56.680
It's a poisonous mushroom

00:17:56.680 --> 00:17:58.810
that bleeds from its cap when injured.

00:18:00.240 --> 00:18:02.120
The killer specifically found this mushroom,

00:18:02.120 --> 00:18:03.760
and he is obsessed with

00:18:03.760 --> 00:18:06.160
striking his victims' heads during the crimes.

00:18:06.160 --> 00:18:07.480
It's hard not to assume

00:18:07.920 --> 00:18:10.520
he's making a metaphor for the previous cases.

00:18:15.080 --> 00:18:16.540
Another elaborate setup.

00:18:17.080 --> 00:18:17.960
This footprint

00:18:18.880 --> 00:18:20.140
is more like a warning.

00:18:21.240 --> 00:18:22.320
It's telling us

00:18:24.240 --> 00:18:25.880
a new round of the game

00:18:26.880 --> 00:18:27.800
is about to begin.